Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:02:04.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed\Nsince a single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi tells that Koza, the\Nleader of the rebel army,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,possesses a passionate heart and will\Nfight to the death for his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's party continues its trek\Nthrough the desert toward Yuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the rebel army is gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Showdown in a Heat Haze!\NAce vs. the Gallant Scorpion"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Popo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tattoo on his back...\NNo question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace! He finally showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Portgas D. Ace! How I've\Nbeen longing for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is all the breakfast we get?!\N--Seconds! Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act wasteful!\NYou've had enough calories!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy! Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Keep your hands off others' food!\N--C'mon! Gimme food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't sweat it!\N--There isn't any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this happen at every meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Ace-san is cleaning his\Nfork and plate after his meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He's completely different...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn you! Give it back!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from his incompetent little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd never guess from\NAce's well-mannered personality
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he has an immense\Nbounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-san has a bounty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's such a large amount\Nthat bounty hunters around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drool at the thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace of the\NWhitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates the world over fear\Nthe mere mention of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means this Blackbeard pirate\NAce-san is seriously chasing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must really be something, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard... The traitor who\Nkilled his own crewmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Ace is going to keep\Nchasing him as long as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start off with a little gift from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I ain't gonna kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:05:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna blow up that\Nrock you're sitting on first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my pride! So my aim\Nis to capture you alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get going! Today--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dammit! Give it back!\N--What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here we go!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry and clean up!\NWe're leaving for Yuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh no! They saw us!\N--Hurry, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This meat can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What're you talking about, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meat's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, meat!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?! This way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good, Chip? It's our first\Nfood in 10 days! Eat it slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we got meat!\NHere, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we never even had\Nany in the Badlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're from the Badlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that rustic nowheresville?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who're you?!\N--You can't have the food back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Move and you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm generally not fond\Nof dangerous things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big brother!\NHave you shot for reals before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really shoot bullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hell if I know!\NH-Hold on! I'm gonna--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play your dangerous games in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good little boys should brush\Ntheir teeth before sleepy-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He bounced it back with a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've never seen\Nanyone so strong before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I want\Nyou to find and catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you catch him,\NI'll pay you a million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pay right away,\Nbut I will pay it when I grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Find this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion-sama's ultimate weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hit from this will\Ndemolish that entire rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, while Ace is buried under\Nthe rubble, I'll capture him alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Light 'er up, Popo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! It's meat, but it\Nran away! I'll make it pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! Why did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strangle ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that blows up, it'll take\Nhalf of Alabasta with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It'll blow the\NGrand Line to the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened to the bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy! Quit laughing and help me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy-daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Where is he?! Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to be playing\Naround at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out to where he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother and I've followed\Nhim out here from the Badlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion. A bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys\Nchasing a bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well...\N--I have business with him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man in Yuba defeated Blackbeard.\NHis name was Scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My reason for going\Nto Yuba is to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! He defeated Blackbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are we going, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very lucky boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to witness me, the world's\Ngreatest upcoming bounty hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,locked in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bounty hunter, old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared when I say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I've been on many\Na heart-pounding adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought epic battles with\Neveryone from Double Barrel Danny
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Hellbattler Luther and they\Nalways begged me for their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but someday it will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, someday, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI'm gonna beat Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else but him would be a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:11:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna beat Ace up,\Nold guy?! That's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Don't mock me, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I do something, I don't kid around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Men live for big ambitions!\NI have to show 'em that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Show who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Scorpion, the gallant man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, Ace. Did this Scorpion\Nguy really beat Blackbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. The only way\Nto find out is to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace? You don't mean the real...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fire Fist Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people. And a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're coming!\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Scorpion! The indomitable hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from afar to challenge you!\NLet's fight, fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Scorpion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! Are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's really him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fire Fist Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! N-No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry! Your luck's run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heroic saga that's\Ntold on the sea ends today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! He's the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so exciting!\NAce! It's a serious fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull any punches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't planning to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something\NI wanna ask him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me?!\NDon't wimp out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!\NI'm invulnerable! I won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as they're waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He sent that metal net flying back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be any fun if it were\Nthat easy to stop Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You seem to have some skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hellish battle is just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popo! Compressed Extinguisher Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A compressed air gun filled\Nwith extinguisher foam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-What?!\N--Extinguisher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use this to fill you full\Nof compressed extinguisher foam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you never had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected as much. You lied about\Nbeating Blackbeard, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You figured using his name would\Nget me to show up. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Not too\Nshabby of a plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've fought on even terms this far.\NNow I'm gonna get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D-Dad"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dip! Chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You don't stand a\Nchance against Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you two doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you leave the Badlands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Look! Look how big this potato is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That is big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky we got to\Neat another potato today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, I wanna eat until I'm full!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't tell Dad that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad gave up his dream of\Nbounty-hunting so he could support us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an incredible hero across\Nthe sea on a big adventure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wonder if there's anything\Nthat exciting for us, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna live our lives\Nwithout anything interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Dad threw away his dream for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to spend our whole\Nlives in this withered land, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of glum look is that?!\NQuit complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch! I'm gonna\Ngo back to bounty-hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to challenge\Nthat hero! Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:17:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm gonna fight the world's\Ngreatest battle and come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's greatest battle\Nis too much for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to get you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly. I'm the\Nworld's greatest bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought epic battles with\Neveryone from Double Barrel Danny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Hellbattler Luther and they\Nall begged for their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so you plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found me out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm a terrible\Nliar and a terrible father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there is one thing that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the most insignificant person
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can still challenge the world's\Ngreatest hero if he tries hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show you two a grand dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men need dreams burning\Ninside their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means struggling every day,\Nnever give up! Stand tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live every day with a laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep challenging the\Nimpossible, life will be paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way to show that\Nwithout putting my life on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! If you stand up,\Nthe path will always open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Watch your father's\Nunconquerable spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as I have an enormous\Ndream burning inside my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popo! The bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace! This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! That's enough! No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dip! Chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We understand! We understand\Nwhat you're trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stood up to hardship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll live every day as hard as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you around,\Nwe're filled with courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I complained!\NI don't really care about food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy just being with you, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We love you, Dad!\N--We love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dip! Chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gum-Gum...\N--I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad protected us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old guy. Did you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could really die and\Nleave my adorable sons behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion-sama is invulnerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to get\Nthis lowly father of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home. To the Badlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really leaving, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as Blackbeard isn't in Alabasta,\NI have no reason to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh.\N--Where will you go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpion says there's a man\Nwho saw him in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always hang on to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's just a scrap of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scrap of paper will bring you\Nand me together again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You don't want it?\N--No, I'll keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for a big brother to\Nworry about his bungling kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a bit much for you to\Nhandle, but take good care of 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. When we next meet,\Nwe'll both be top pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-san certainly was\Na mysterious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You ladies prefer mysterious men?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enigmatic, too!\NMy left eye, for example!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did he say?\NTranslate, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! They're gone!\N--Don't tell me they got separated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins and Lost Ways!\NVivi, Her Friends, and the Country's Form"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
