Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:02:04.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed\Nsince a single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi, in an attempt to\Nstop an orchestrated rebellion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,decides to talk with the\Nleader of the rebel army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruined Erumalu behind her,\Nshe now heads straight for Yuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Spiders Café at 8 O'Clock--\NThe Enemy Leaders Gather"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did your brother give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's just a scrap of paper.\N--Just a scrap of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is just a scrap of paper.\NIt's not even a note or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give me your hat, Luffy!\N--Huh? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that important, I'll sew it to\Nthe underside of your hat ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Great! Sew it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you go!\N--Thanks! Now I don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing written on it.\NWhat point is there to keeping it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace told me to keep it, so I'm keeping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your confidence isn't based on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? It's right a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't know about that...\N--Someone carry me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Yuba is just over those big rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make one more push to get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yuba, huh?!\N--Yep! Yuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Carry me, Zoro...\N--Don't be a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ooh! Carry me too, Zoro!\N--Rock-paper-scissors, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation will commence\Nat high noon two days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished the arrangements?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everything has gone smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,150 Billions are on standby in Nanohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also called Mr. 2 back.\NIt appears he failed to capture Mr. 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The officer agents' gathering is at\N8:00 tonight, at the Spiders Café...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is past 5:00 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:05:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume they'll start\Ngathering around now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes!\NMerry Christmas! Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a long, exhausting trip!\NMy back's killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:28.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miss Merry Christmas"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! It's all your fault, Mr. 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your slowness is backache-inducing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! How's business, Paula?\NThe place is empty today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Place empty! Plempty! Ple! It's ple!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you again.\NWelcome, Miss Merry Christmas, Mr. 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:56.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Paula"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the shop all to yourselves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make you some orange pekoe\Nand... apple tea, was it, Mr. 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the hot drinks! I want\Nsomething I can drink right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some right away! Right away!\NRight now! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem lively. How is work going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my trade, screw up and you die!\NThings are going great, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You imbecile! Imbecile! Imbe! Imb! Im!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--? What kind of crazy\Nsongs does this place play now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Song? No, I have a sonata playing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your fingertip with your nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep with your fingernails!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Un, deux!\N--Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before... being born...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson! Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love... and mascara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mascara with a nosebleed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm self-made!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So... Lesson!\N--Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lesson!\N--Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, the greatest!\N--The greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are deux lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not stupid, Paula!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm a dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--One Octopar, please!\N--Octopar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break! An Octopus\NParfait! Everyone knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, you guys can leave now!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lazy with your dance practice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Un, deux! Un, deux...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Fatty! Old hag! You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your trap, you! Pipe down,\Nyou're hurting my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, I hear even\NMr. 1's team is being mobilized!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met 'em for whatever\Nreason, so I just can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The night grows ever later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost the appointed time of 8:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored I spin around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll take a spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it! You're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, hag?!\NYou wanna fight or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now! Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, now! What happened to you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come bursting back in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... It was him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. They're acquaintances of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were acting suspiciously\Nin the desert, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I doubt they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be on rather close terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but worthless, cozy relationships\Nwill only result in your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These men are my subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Mr. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, Deux, Krah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, Deux, Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bold Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un! Deux!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?! He slipped through the wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He shattered the wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! That's enough, Mr. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, Miss Doublefinger.\NI'm going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Let go of me, Fatty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2! Cool your anger as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's now 8:00. All the agents\Nthat should be here are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a letter with orders has\Narrived at the Spiders Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're to head to Rainbase,\Nthe city of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man we call boss, the man\Nwhose face we've never seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is waiting for us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be on their\Nway here to Rainbase now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Bunchi to get them. I expect\Nthem to arrive sometime tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you were\Nactually Miss Doublefinger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:10.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miss Doublefinger"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember ever saying that I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found replacements for\Nthe Billions wiped out in Nanohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished assigning the replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've dispatched the Lizard Runners\Nto contact the new Billions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Everything is progressing smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up ahead! I see a light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we make it to Yuba?!\NI can't really see with all this sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that sound be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city doesn't look right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sandstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of Yuba is being\Nstruck by a sandstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. It's almost no\Ndifferent from that Erumalu city!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this supposed to be\Nan oasis city, Vivi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sand has raised the ground!\NThe oasis has been swallowed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you travelers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted from\Nyour trek through the desert...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. This town is a bit dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're free to rest here if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of inns here.\NThey are this town's pride, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, we came because we heard\Nthe rebel army was in this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you\Nhave with the rebel army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! Don't tell me you're\Nhoping to join the rebellion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for those fools,\Nthey left town long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sandstorm hit the town just now,\Nbut it certainly wasn't the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sand has dried up\Nafter three years of drought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sandstorms began to\Nfrequent this town ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, the oasis of\Nthe past was swallowed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving what you see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the town's flow of supplies gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not even the rebel army's protracted\Nstruggle would have worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rebel army moved its base to Katorea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katorea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that, Vivi?! Is Katorea close by?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an oasis next to Nanohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katorea is the town where\NI got lost and met Lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When you saved me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lashes says he was carrying\Nrebel army goods to Katorea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why didn't you say so sooner!\N--Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whatever!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we come all this way, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "Vivi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, old guy! Vivi isn't the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell him that, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan? Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I can't blame you.\NI did lose some weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto-ojisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Vivi-chan. This is goodbye for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit sometime,\Nonce the city's taken shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Toto-ojisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba will surely make this kingdom lusher...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto-ojisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan. I have faith in His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone who would\Never betray the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rebellion is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if it hasn't rained\Nfor a mere three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in His Majesty.\NMost of the country still does, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many times I tried to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they won't listen to anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebellion won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their strength is at its limit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to settle things\Nonce and for all in the next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their backs are to the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're prepared to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Vivi-chan! Stop those fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:37.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where's our leader?\N--Inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Toto-ojisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will stop the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Vivi-chan. This is goodbye for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit sometime,\Nonce the city's taken shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Toto-ojisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna make an awesome city
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make this kingdom even lusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Vivi! Grow up to be a great princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've contacted everyone in the other towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. The time to strike has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We don't have nearly\Nenough weapons, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no other choice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who can\Nprotect this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands, and the sand\Nand time that spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is what\NI was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kick Crocodile's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really knows how to get\Nstraight to the point sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! You want it so nobody dies in this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't you think that's soft-hearted?\N--Hold on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least put all our lives on the line together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy vs. Vivi! The Tearful Vow\Nto Put Friends on the Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
