Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:02:04.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rainbase"                 "Alubarna"\N      "Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"\N"Spiders Café"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed\Nsince a single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stop the maelstrom of war\Nspreading throughout Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi was in a rush\Nto talk with the rebel army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna kick Crocodile's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stop the people rebelling,\Nwill that stop Crocodile?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least try putting all of our\Nlives on the line together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where Crocodile is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was at this moment\Nthat Vivi made up her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battlefront of Alabasta!\NRainbase, the City of Dreams"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san is exactly right.\NI've made up my mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to where Crocodile is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That does seem to be\Nthe quickest shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning no more of this\Nannoying, roundabout traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is this damn Crocodile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the capital city of Alubarna,\Nwhere my father rules from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the rebel army is currently here,\Npreparing to invade Alubarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to take care of\NCrocodile before that can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile is here. Rainbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbase...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about a day's journey north of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, I told you to\Nquit moaning, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you to say anything\Nwhen you're riding the camel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let us ride, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You camel-woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-mel!\N--Good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! You haven't collapsed today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm gonna try extra hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi. Does Rainbase have water?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's no problem there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gambling town, almost\Ncompletely detached from the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Gambling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! What're you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even here in Alabasta\Nthere are carefree cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum No Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gimme some!\N--Gum-Gum No Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Just one sip!\NThat is why we have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:05:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dry old guy spent all\Nnight digging this water up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just drink it like\Nit's nothing! You dumbhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Sometimes you\Ncan restrain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't take another step... W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?! How long until Rainbase?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I never would've been able\Nto make this decision on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then gimme food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I kick Crocodile's ass,\Ngimme so much food I might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:43.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rebel Army Camp in Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Koza! Let me join the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! I have the right to\Njoin the rebellion too, don't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I despise the king! Let me fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him, Faracla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got this trying to protect me\Nin the middle of a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to see the\Nmedical wards and the graves too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That doesn't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Towns've dried up, and many have\Ndied 'cause the king stole the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made lots of my friends sick, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the king's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of getting hurt or even dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave. Our opinions are too different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all afraid, and none\Nof us want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that we wanted to. We had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the country wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you understand or not,\Nit has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said leave, dammit!\NThis is no place for children!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about, Koza?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to rant\Nand rave at children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like looking at my\Nold self. It made me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't changed one bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we gathered enough weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's proving difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact all the other towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we have weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we launch an all-out assault on Alubarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sire! It's only a matter of time until\Nthe rebel army attacks Alubarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must take action first,\Nbefore it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! I told you no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a children's quarrel!\NIs retaliation what you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Sire! The country's\Nexistence hangs in the balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the Dance Powder\Nincident, it has been clear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that someone is trying\Nto destroy our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suggesting\Nwe destroy our countrymen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before learning who's\Nreally pulling the strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the downfall of our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! A country is its people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this wire-puller has\Nnot shown himself whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking action after this unknown\Nshadow devours our country
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be too late, Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king won't allow us\Nto take the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can barely even appease\Nthe soldiers at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Igaram-san were\Nhere at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram says he's leaving\Nthe country for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we speak, he and Vivi-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are probably still hard at work,\Ntrying to figure out who's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka-sama! Pell-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo has?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sire! Who is that letter from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vivi's handwriting, without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sire! Does that mean--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo came to deliver\Na letter from Vivi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father. Everything written\Nhere is true. It is fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person trying to bring\Nsuffering and ruin to this kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is none other than Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram is another who has\Nfallen at the hands of Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile! I stupidly believed\Nhe worked for the government!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would've imagined he\Nwas trying to usurp this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave his life for\NVivi-sama and this land...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, there are people who\Nhave given me unfathomable power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I continue with them, we may\Nmake a difference in this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light of hope is here!\NAlabasta will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have faith, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says you fought valiantly,\Ntoo, Karoo. You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurt? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this thing on our left arm\Nis the sign of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know the enemy's identity!\NPrepare the soldiers for expedition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let Vivi's resolve\Nand Igaram's death be for naught!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking immediate action!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to Rainbase,\Nwhere Crocodile is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Sire! Rainbase is\Ntoo far away to be "immediate"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile has the citizens on his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more so than you,\Nwith all due respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we attack Rainbase,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rebel army will use that as\Na chance to storm the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that happens--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if the rebel army\Ndestroys this palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you before! A country is its people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if our royal army falls,\Nas long as Crocodile is defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the country will be reborn by the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, consider if we clash\Nwith the rebel army instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile is the only one\Nwho will have the last laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that dedicated to--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if by some chance\Nthe rebel army doesn't stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need only take out Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against one of the\NSeven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile is not weak of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle will not be without\Nsacrifices before its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka! I'm holding a war meeting!\NAssemble the officers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pell! Go on ahead and\Nconduct enemy reconnaissance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we've been severely\Nunderestimating His Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What powerful spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We go to battle tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending all soldiers to Rainbase!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Are we here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Time to beat up Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Rainbase!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, does Baroque Works\Nknow we're in this country now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did run into Mr. 2, so we should\Nassume they know we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know what we look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do much of anything\Nwhile we're in Rainbase!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get spotted first,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile can probably deal\Nwith us in all kinds of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassination is their area of specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you even listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, no matter who we run into,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Nami-san and Vivi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two girls can call me "Prince"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Prince... Water...\N--Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water! Need water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Water! Water!\N--Wait! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take money with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think the Straw Hats\Nwill show up here, in Rainbase?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Call it a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We can get water here, Usopp!\N--Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, something stinks about this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get a strong sense that something\Nbig is lurking in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A barrel of water! No, five!\NFive barrels of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you think there\Nreally is a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between the Baroque Works criminal\Norganization and Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here!\N--Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is that Straw Hat\Nis out to get Crocodile...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...one of the Seven Warlords.\N--This water's great, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and take the others some!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really count on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can do little errands\Njust fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. I bet they'll come back\Nwith a bunch of trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do warm-up exercises if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Run!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Got that barrel?!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going after 'em, Tashigi!\NGather the marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, how much do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know those kids, you better\Npay for the water they took, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! I'm sorry for the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Navy here again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's chasing 'em again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are they running this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say! Tony-kun hasn't come back yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him! He'll manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one bringing them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch 'em for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're quick to run away, I'll give 'em that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works is gonna spot us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we run through the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--To where Crocodile is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Vivi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Do you see that\Nalligator-roof building up ahead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the casino Crocodile runs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raindinners!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, huh?!\NSo that's where Crocodile is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be best if we split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet at the alligator house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They split up!\N--Don't let 'em escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me, Smokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got real guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can keep running forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Luffy's smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Zoro's smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji's goes that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Bushido! This direction, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them! No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baroque Works Millions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stuck between the devil\Nand the deep sea," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N--R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look after Nami-san!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold 'em off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright! You can count on me!\N--Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go!\N--We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without that smoke freak around,\Nthey're just small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Mr. Bushido will be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you got?\NTry again some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro! We meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing,\Ncutting down regular citizens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I got my own circumstances, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have no desire to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We settled our match in Loguetown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even laid a single blow yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like her! Way too much like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And quit it with that face, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come again?! Are you trying\Nto ridicule me yet again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! She's the one\Nperson I can't deal with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Up ahead!\NThe entrance to Raindinners!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the middle of a lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is no one here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's blast 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start with those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Vivi with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Is she not here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might've gone inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plume-Plume is with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's go! Run inside, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Vivi and the pirates\Nare here in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We just received\Nword from the Millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go welcome the foolish rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Crocodile!\NI'm going to kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands, and the sand\Nand time that spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is what\NI was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile! Come out! I came\Nto Alubarna to kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna make him\Ncome out! You're so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against the kingdom's hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna make these\Ncustomers our enemies too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But without Vivi,\Nwe don't know who Crocodile is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.99,0:23:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Come to think of it, where is Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Trap of Certain Defeat!\NStorming Raindinners"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
